{"type": "article", "id": 3463, "title": "Alessi 开瓶器", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-12T07:23:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232828BX059kGMNJlDhZLd.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t英国 Shiro 建筑事务所的设计师 Andrea Morgante 日前受意大利家居品牌 Alessi 委托，为意大利啤酒品牌 Peroni Nastro Azzurro 设计了一款开瓶器「Fuso」。受到 Peroni Nastro Azzurro 品牌 logo 的启发，设计师模仿其 logo 上那条飘动的蓝色丝带图案，设计了一款扭曲着的不锈钢长条，给人一种流动的感觉，中间为鼓起的镂空部分，而两边细长的手握的部分则更容易让使用者施力。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232827PaF7y9Gx3HoDsJw0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232827U51riBhWNopwlukE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232828JTe5MlBv7IjXUhYR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.853125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}